---
import Layout from "../layouts/TabPage.astro";
---

<Layout title="RSVP" description="Link to RSVP">
  <div class="text-container">
    <p>
      If you're planning on attending, we're very excited to see you! Check back here later on for a formal RSVP once we finalize the schedule.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you won't be able to attend, we understand! We'd love for everyone invited to be able to be there, but we know it's a big commitment. 
      We ask that you please reach out to us to let us know so that we can plan accordingly.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
